<html>

<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" data-inline="data-inline">
</head>

<body>
  <p class="preheader">
    Please complete the following before your first day of class:
  </p>
  <div class="container">
    <header class="mcad-frame">
      MCAD <img class="logo" src="https://canvas.mcad.edu/img/MCAD_X_logo.png" alt="X" width="16" height="16" />
      ONLINE
      LEARNING
    </header>

    <main>
      <header class="email-header">
        <div class="header-image">ðŸ¤©</div>
        <h1><strong>Get Ready</strong> for Your Online Course</h1>
      </header>

      <p>Hello {{ firstName }},</p>

      <p>The start of your online course is right around the corner:</p>

      <div class="info-box course-info">
        <p><b>{{courseName}} ({{term}} {{year}})</b></p>
        <p>{{courseCode}} â€¢ {{credits}}</p>
        <p>{{startDate}} â€“ {{endDate}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>To prepare, please complete the following before your first day of class.</p>

      <h2>Step 1</h2>

      <p>Before your first day <a href="https://learn.mcad.edu/orientation">complete the Blackboard Orientation</a>
      </p>

      <p><a class="button" href="https://learn.mcad.edu/orientation">Begin Blackboard Orientation</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        You'll learn how to login to Blackboard, what a typical online course looks like,
        where you can get books and supplies, and more.
      </p>

      <h2>Step 2</h2>

      <p>Make sure you can login to Blackboard at <a href="https://learn.mcad.edu">learn.mcad.edu</a> using your
        MCAD credentials.</p>

      <p><a class="button" href="https://learn.mcad.edu">Login to Blackboard</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Don't have a password yet?</h2>

      <p>
        You can set (or reset) your password
        with the following info:
      </p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p class="key-value">
          <b class="key">Link</b>
          <code><a href="https://password.mcad.edu/index.php?selfservice=forgotpw">Reset Password</a>
          </p>
          <p class="key-value">
            <b class="key">Username</b>
            <code class="value">{{username}}</code>
        </p>
        <p class="key-value">
          <b class="key">Student ID#</b>
          <code class="value">{{id}}</code>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>If you cannot login, please email <a href="mailto:online@mcad.edu">online@mcad.edu</a> for assistance.</p>

      <h2>
        Can't See Your Course? Don't Worry!
      </h2>
      <p>Your course will not be available until after your course open date:</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <p class="key-value">
          <b class="key">Course Opens</b>
          <code class="value">{{ openDate }}</code>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>After your course opens, login to Blackboard at <a href="https://learn.mcad.edu">learn.mcad.edu</a>.</p>

      <h2>Questions? Need Help?</h2>
      <p>Contact MCAD Online Learning</p>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <p><a href="mailto:online@mcad.edu">online@mcad.edu</a></p>
        <p><a href="tel:6128743618">612-874-3618</a></p>
        <p><a href="tel:18008746233">1-800-874-MCAD (6233)</a> â€“ press 4 for Online Learning</p>
      </div>
      <p>Have a great semester!</p>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>

